Package: lettercase
Title: Utilities for formatting character vectors as lower case, UPPER CASE,
    Title Case, snake_case, Cap Words, etc.
Version: 0.9.1
Authors@R: "Christopher Brown <chris.brown@decisionpatterns.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: Utilities for formatting and manipulating character vectors for
    cases such as snake_case, Title Case, UPPERCASE,
    lower case, etc.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0),
